#. type: Plain text
#: upstream/_versions/2.7/guides/picocli.adoc:39
msgid "Simple PicocliApplication with only one `Command` can be created as follows:"
msgstr "`Command` を 1 つだけ使ったシンプルな PicocliApplication は、以下のように作成できます。"

#. type: delimited block -
#: upstream/_versions/2.7/guides/picocli.adoc:43
#: upstream/_versions/2.7/guides/picocli.adoc:103
#: upstream/_versions/2.7/guides/picocli.adoc:138
